          <a href="https://wa.me/6281234567890?text=Halo%20kak%2C%20saya%20ingin%20konsultasi%20tentang%20Hukum%20Perdata" class="btn btn-whatsapp" target="_blank"> hubungi via WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Perjanjian Riba</h3>
          <p>Konsultasi dan pendampingan hukum terkait perjanjian riba, pembiayaan, dan masalah keuangan Islam. Kami memastikan keabsahan perjanjian Anda sesuai syariat.</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/6281234567890?text=Halo%20kak%2C%20saya%20ingin%20konsultasi%20tentang%20Perjanjian%20Riba" class="btn btn-whatsapp" target="_blank"> hubungi via WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div>
          <h3>雷法学院</h3>
          <p>Jl. Sudirman No. 123</p>
          <p>Jakarta Selatan</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Kontak</h3>
          <p>📞 +62 812 3456 7890</p>
          <p>✉️ info@lawfirm.co.id</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 雷法学院. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>